      "turn_id": 1,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "我们需要画一个服务保护系统的架构图。核心是一个Controller，它要接收两类信号：Health Signals和Confirmation Signals，然后根据策略去调整Agent的负载倍数。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Controller",
        "Health Signals",
        "Confirmation Signals",
        "Service Protection Policy",
        "Agent",
        "Adjust load multiplier"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 2,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "明白了。Health Signals和Confirmation Signals都是指向Controller的输入对吧？还有，Agent那边是不是要处理客户端的入站请求？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Health Signals",
        "Confirmation Signals",
        "Controller",
        "Client",
        "Incoming requests",
        "Agent"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 3,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "对，Client发Incoming requests到Agent。Agent内部有个Req Queue，用三个方括号表示待处理的packets。然后Agent把处理完的req/s发给下游Service。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Client",
        "Incoming requests",
        "Agent",
        "Req Queue",
        "packets",
        "req/s",
        "Service"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 4,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "好，我先画个草稿：Controller用橙色，Agent和Service用绿色，信号用浅色边框。Health Signals和Confirmation Signals都连到Controller，Controller通过Adjust load multiplier控制Agent。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Controller",
        "Agent",
        "Service",
        "Health Signals",
        "Confirmation Signals",
        "Adjust load multiplier"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 5,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "repair",
      "utterance": "等等，Service Protection Policy应该是放在Controller子图内部的，不是单独的一个节点。还有packets那个[] [] []要放在Req Queue子图里。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Service Protection Policy",
        "Controller",
        "packets",
        "Req Queue"
      ],
      "is_repair": true
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 6,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "调整了，Service Protection Policy现在嵌在Controller子图里，packets也放进Agent下面的Req Queue子图了。Client到Agent、Agent到Service的关系都保留。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Service Protection Policy",
        "Controller",
        "packets",
